# G mock

Generate or refresh testify mocks.

1. Ask the user for `<InterfaceName>` (or `--all` to refresh every
   mock, or `--check` for CI drift gate).
2. Run `gofasta g mock <args> --json`.
3. If `--check` reports `MOCK_DRIFT`, the user has updated an
   interface but not regenerated the mock ‚Äî re-run without
   `--check` to refresh.
